Name: FHIR Restful Interactions
Title: null
Descriptino: The set of interactions defined by the RESTful part of the FHIR specification.

Name: AuditEventEntityRole
Title: AuditEventEntityRole
Descriptino: Code representing the role the entity played in the audit event.

Name: IdentifierType
Title: identifierType
Descriptino: HL7-defined code system of concepts specifying type of identifier. Used in HL7 Version 2.x messaging data types CX, PLN, PPN, XCN and XON.

Name: ObservationValue
Title: ObservationValue
Descriptino: This code system covers all concepts of HL7-defined values for the Observation value element, when it has a coded datatype.

Name: ParticipationType
Title: ParticipationType
Descriptino: A code specifying the meaning and purpose of every Participation instance. Each of its values implies specific constraints on the Roles undertaking the participation.

Name: AuthZsubType
Title: Authorization subType events
Descriptino: These AuditEvent subTypes are related to Authorization Decisions. These are more specific types of Security Alert.

Name: BasicAuditEntityType
Title: Entity Types that are defined in IHE BasicAudit
Descriptino: These are new codes used in BasicAudit IG, where AuditEvent.entity is used to hold a specific kind of data that is not covered by the existing valueSet.

Name: OtherIdentifierTypes
Title: OtherId Identifier Types
Descriptino: OtherId Types beyond those in the FHIR core

Name: UserAgentTypes
Title: The code used to identifiy a User Agent
Descriptino: Code used to identify the User Agent. Defined codes for SAML vs OAuth to enable differentiation of .policy as the token ID
